sources.title: Deceit | Full Movie | Mystery Thriller | Emmanuelle Chriqui
sources.description:
Deceit - Dave returns to the hometown he abandoned. His best friends, Emily and Brian, are now married, but he hears rumors that Brian is a violent alcoholic. Dave, thinking that Emily is in an abusive relationship, accidentally kills him. Dave finds compromising photos of him and Emily and that Emily is not only having an affair with him. Not everyone is who they appear to be.
2006.  Stars: Emmanuelle Chriqui, Matt Long, Luke Mably
